            %dt Custom research
            %dd Our blend of tech and people, build custom contact lists on the fly.
          %dl
            %dt Plug &amp; play data
            %dd Data is imported to any CRM or automation tool as often as you need new contacts.
          %dl
            %dt Pay as you go
            %dd Plans are built for scrapp startups and emerging enterprises, who need flexibility.

