          %h4 Accelerate awareness, inbound traffic and thought leadership with content in the right places.
          %p Referral traffic is the cheapest acquistion channel in the game. We plan, develop and distribute your content to the right channels.
          %dl
            %dt Press Lists
            %dd We generate fresh contacts weekly based on your custom goals and product.
          %dl
            %dt Guest Posts
            %dd Our SDRR team manages cold outreach to your top contacts through drip campaigns.
          %dl
            %dt Content Promotion
            %dd Analytics provide insights to potpimize value props, sales cycle and product fit.
        #tab3.content{style: 'opacity: 0'}
          %h4 We accelerate revenue and build early traction with turnkey sales development services.
